.TH KINGPEPED 1
.SH NAME
kingpeped \- KingPepe Core daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B kingpeped
[\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B kingpeped
daemon connects to the KingPepe peer-to-peer network, validates blocks and
transactions, maintains the local chainstate, and exposes JSON-RPC when server
mode is enabled.
.SH OPTIONS
Run
.B kingpeped -help
for the complete option list supported by this build.
.SH FILES
The default data directory is
.B ~/.kingpepe
on Linux,
.B ~/Library/Application Support/Kingpepe
on macOS, and
.B %APPDATA%\\Kingpepe
on Windows.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR kingpepe-cli (1),
.BR kingpepe-qt (1)
